Private Function getUTCTimeOffset() Dim localTime As Date Dim utcTime As Date
'Time in Events database is recorded as UTC time, thus Local time must be transformed into UTC time. localTime = Now GetSystemTime oUTC utcTime = DateSerial(oUTC.wYear, oUTC.wMonth, oUTC.wDay) + TimeSerial(oUTC.wHour, oUTC.wMinute, oUTC.wSecond) getUTCOffsetHours = DateDiff("h", localTime, utcTime) End Function
Private Sub btnFiltersApply_Released() On Error Resume Next Dim whereClause As String Dim utcTimeOffset As Integer
'Time in Events database is recorded as UTC time, thus Local time must be transformed into UTC time. utcTimeOffset = getUTCTimeOffset() whereClause = "EventTimeStamp BETWEEN " & Format(DateAdd("h", utcTimeOffset, dataDeInicio), "'yyyy-mm-dd HH:mm:ss'") & _ " AND " & Format(DateAdd("h", utcTimeOffset, DateAdd("d", 1, dataFinal)), "'yyyy-mm-dd HH:mm:ss'")
FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.whereClause = whereClause End Sub
Private Sub ExecuteFTAE_FilterCommandByAreaName(areaName As String) Select Case TagPrioridade Case 0 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(Area" & areaName & ")") Case 1 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(Area" & areaName & "Todos)") Case 2 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(Area" & areaName & "Alta)") Case 3 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(Area" & areaName & "Media)") Case 4 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(Area" & areaName & "Baixa)") Case 5 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(Area" & areaName & "Eventos)") End Select End Sub
Private Sub ExecuteFTAE_FilterCommandByPriority(priorityName As String) Select Case TagArea Case 0 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(Prioridade" & priorityName & ")") Case 1 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(AreaTodos" & priorityName & ")") Case 2 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(AreaOleo" & priorityName & ")") Case 3 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(AreaGas" & priorityName & ")") Case 4 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(AreaSeguranca" & priorityName & ")") Case 5 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(AreaEletrica" & priorityName & ")") Case 6 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(AreaSistemasGerais" & priorityName & ")") Case 7 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(AreaAutomacao" & priorityName & ")") Case 8 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.FilterName(AreaAgua" & priorityName & ")") End Select End Sub
